text: Naho Hoshiyama (born 25 December 1980) is a Japanese gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tokyo
